STATE
v.
Andre' E. WILLIAMS. No. 184P07. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 8, 2007. Charles E. Reece, Assistant Attorney General, Scott Thomas, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 18th day of April 2007 by Defendant for Probable Cause Hearings:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 8th day of November 2007."
